title: Santa Cruz Product Pillage with Justin Strubing
description: In this Product Pillage, Justin Strubing loots the NHS warehouse for the latest goodies from his sponsors: Santa Cruz Skateboards, Krux Trucks and OJ Wheels. Afterwards, Justin gets in a sesh with Blake Johnson, Josh Borden and Ron Whaley.
